text: Kandal is a province in Cambodia. Its capital and largest city is Ta Khmao. Kandal Province completely surrounds the national capital Phnom Penh. The province has two of the biggest rivers in the country, the Bassac and Mekong Rivers. There are 10 districts and 1 municipality: *Angk Snuol *Kandal Stueng *Kaoh Thum *Khsach Kandal *Kien Svay *Leuk Daek *Lvea Aem *Mukh Kampul *Ponhea Lueu *S'ang *Ta Khmau Municipality Category:Provinces of Cambodia Category:Establishments in Cambodia Category:1907 establishments in Asia
title: Kandal province
